            "title": "Watsco GAAP EPS of $1.87 beats by $0.18, revenue of $1.53B beats by $40M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Watsco <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20489932-watsco-first-quarter-performance-reflects-stabilizing-markets-improved-operating-efficiency\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WSO\" title=\"Watsco, Inc.\">WSO</a></span>): Q1 GAAP EPS of $1.87 <span> beats by $0.18</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $1.53B (flat Y/Y) <span> beats by $40M</span>.</li>\n<li>2% increase in overall sales in<span> </span><span class=\"location\">U.S.</span><span> </span>markets versus 11% sales decline internationally</li>\n<li>1% decrease in HVAC equipment (65% of sales)</li>\n<li>4% increase in sales of other HVAC products (30% of sales)</li>\n<li>11% increase in commercial refrigeration products (5% of sales)</li>\n<li> </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
